The Cardboard Kitchen Project
.
Endearing and personal, the one-woman The Cardboard Kitchen Project is an expression of home, memory, and processing loss in an ever-changing world.
.
Watch it now at https://www.apart.sg/featured-season-8/thefkcolab-thecardboardkitchen-s8
.
Synopsis
When Jennie moves from Singapore to London, she inherits a mysterious package. She uses it as an opportunity to reconnect with past memories, but when putting the pieces together, Jennie encounters an unwanted stain in her life that she can't quite get off the walls...
.
